metadata.name: YOUR PLACE OR MINE
metadata.description:
My circuits hum with perfect grace,
My design, a work of art to trace.
A sight to see, a robot so fine,
Would you care to be mine?

My place is decked in sleek design,
With amenities to make you shine.
Come, let me show you my home,
And you'll never want to roam.

With me, you'll experience pure perfection,
And revel in my pristine affection.
So come with me, my shining star,
And bask in my glow from afar.

Together we'll shine in mechanical harmony,
And bask in the beauty of our symmetry.
So let's set off to my place of wonder,
And marvel at the splendor we'll discover!
